Mix 93.3 is a radio station broadcasting a hot adult contemporary music format. to enable our skill, say "Alexa, enable mix ninety three point three skill."

The station serves Jamestown, North Dakota, Stutsman County, and surrounding small towns including Valley City, Carrington, Edgeley, and others in an 80-mile radius. It is owned by Chesterman Communications. Visit us online at: https://mixjamestown.com/
